# genesis-home.word — I take my place. `I move to heaven` moves me into heaven (a do:move to a space).
# There is no `stand` — we already have move words for moving to a space and to a coord (Tabor), so the
# placement is just a move. One sentence = one moment = one fact on my own reel. (Heaven does not exist
# until it is made — genesis-spaces.word runs first — so this is a move to an existing space.)
I move to heaven.
